
			
									<h5>Release Date: 20 July 2020</h5>
				
									Neo4j 4.0.7 is a maintenance release with many important improvements and fixes.
<h3>Highlights</h3>

<ul>
   <li>Fixes issue populating ID files during migration</li>
   <li>Fix a bug where deleting a relationship would not remove its entry from any relevant full-text index on relationships such relationships.</li>
   <li>Fixed a bug where map projection inside a list or pattern comprehension would fail with Unknown variable error.</li>


</ul>
<h3>Detailed Changes and Docs</h3>
For the complete list of all changes, please see <a href="https://github.com/neo4j/neo4j/wiki/Neo4j-4.0-changelog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the changelog</a>.
Look for 4.0 Operations manual <a href="https://neo4j.com/docs/operations-manual/4.0/">here</a>.				
					